<h3>Hi, <%= @survey.contact.name %>.</h3>

<p>
You have tested <span class="has-text-danger">positive</span> for COVID-19. Here's what you do next:
</p>

<hr>

<article class="media">
  <div class="media-left">
    <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
    <rect width="48" height="48" fill="url(#pattern-house)"/>
    <defs>
    <pattern id="pattern-house" patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox" width="1" height="1">
    <use xlink:href="#image-house" transform="scale(0.0208333)"/>
    </pattern>
    <image id="image-house" width="48" height="48" xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"/>
    </defs>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="media-content">
    <p>
      <strong>Self-isolate</strong> for 7 days or until 3 days after your
      symptoms have completely resolved.
    </p>
  </div>
</article>

<hr>

<article class="media">
  <div class="media-left">
    <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
    <rect width="48" height="48" fill="url(#pattern-doctor)"/>
    <defs>
    <pattern id="pattern-doctor" patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox" width="1" height="1">
    <use xlink:href="#image-doctor" transform="scale(0.0208333)"/>
    </pattern>
    <image id="image-doctor" width="48" height="48" xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"/>
    </defs>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="media-content">
    <p>
      <strong>Monitor your symptoms.</strong> If they get worse, call your doctor
      to seek guidance before going to the hospital.
    </p>
  </div>
</article>

<hr>

<article class="media">
  <div class="media-left">
    <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
    <rect width="48" height="48" fill="url(#pattern-people)"/>
    <defs>
    <pattern id="pattern-people" patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox" width="1" height="1">
    <use xlink:href="#image-people" transform="scale(0.0208333)"/>
    </pattern>
    <image id="image-people" width="48" height="48" xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"/>
    </defs>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="media-content">
    <p>
      <strong>Help identify contacts</strong> you interacted with when you were
      infectious to help stop the spread.
    </p>
  </div>
</article>

<hr>

<p>
We will reach out to reported contacts to ask them to quarantine for 14 days.
We will <strong>never</strong> share information about you to your contacts.
</p>

<p>
  <%= link_to "Take the 15-minute survey", survey_step_path(1), class: "button is-primary is-fullwidth" %>
</p>
